Garoux provides research and AI consulting to accelerate your business. Please contact us to learn more.
We unlock the business value in your company's data.

We provide consulting in data science and machine learning with a focus on measurement and improvement of your core business metrics. We work with you to develop clear, transparent, and achievable goals which have a direct impact on your business.
Garoux is a small consulting group with expertise in machine learning, artificial intelligence, and software development. We know what it takes for AI to get from prototype to production.

Data offers enormous potential to inform business leaders, optimize business operations, and augment workflows with automated intelligence. It can be used to inform large scale strategic decisions, optimize micro decision making and targeting, and enable unique product features. Capitalizing on this potential is difficult, but we can help. We are well versed in all of these use cases, and we will work with you to develop a data strategy which fits your business.

Machine learning transforms data into decisions. It can optimize targeting, personalize content, and dynamically allocate resources for maximum effectiveness. But machine learning also requires an upfront investment, and taking the right first steps is critical to long term success. We will guide you through that process, minimize investment overhead, and demonstrate tangible results at each step along the way.

In many cases, current technology will not be able to automate all the functions that your business needs. By combining machine learning with human centered design, we can build applications which leverage data to improve the effectiveness of your employees. AI can provide automatic fault detection and notifications, improved search functionality for your internal documents, and more. We have a proven track record developing AI integrated applications. We will manage the full development process and deliver on the promise of AI.
Learn what AI can do for you.
We'll help you make it real.

He will help you explore your data, create a strategy, and execute on it from prototype to production.
